Interface EntityPropertyFilter.Inclusive

  • All Superinterfaces:

    Enclosing interface:

    public static interface EntityPropertyFilter.Inclusive
extends EntityPropertyFilter, Collection<String>

    Sub interface stating that the property filter declares all included properties explicitly. Also a Collection that can be iterated for the property names that should be included.

    See the implementation details in EntityPropertyRegistrySupport.
